name: Project-Hum
address: 16, Gasper Enclave, St. John Road, Pali Hill, Mumbai, Mumbai
description: Project Hum is a F&B-Casual Dining outlet that offers a unique dining experience. It is a place where people can come together to enjoy delicious food, drinks, and conversation. The menu features a variety of dishes from around the world, including classic favorites and innovative creations. The atmosphere is relaxed and inviting, with a focus on creating a warm and welcoming environment. The staff is friendly and attentive, ensuring that each guest has a pleasant and enjoyable experience. Project Hum is the perfect place to gather with friends and family for a delicious meal and a great time.
